{"type": "article", "id": 4694, "title": "黄叶吊床", "description": "", "date": "2014-12-25T08:01:01Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 1329, "comment_count": 1, "praise_count": 7, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160605233507c2XHp014rQxYBgO9.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t吊床曾经被用作水手在军舰火炮甲板上的睡床。如今，大多数人对吊床的印象是用来放松，享受美好生活的工具。而吊床品牌 Yellow Leaf 的创始人 Joe Demin 与Rachel Connors 则更进一步，把美好生活也带给吊床背后的劳作者。这款名为「 Vineyard Haven」的吊床便选用了海军蓝条纹的设计元素，用来呼应其最早的用途。Vineyard Haven 由泰国农村未脱离贫困的编织工匠手作而成，他们选用了最柔软的纱线进行编织，为的是使用户身体的每一个部分都能感到舒适。而消费者的每一次购买行为都直接帮助了当地的家庭和社区，使他们获得有益的、可持续的就业机会，从而帮助消除赤贫。定价 179 美元（约合人民币 1113 元），<a href=\"http://www.yellowleafhammocks.com/collections/classic-double-hammock/products/double-hammock-nautical-seersucker-vineyard-haven\" target=\"_blank\">点击这里尝试购买</a>。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605233505IA3ONikYRd7Kr08g.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.7140625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605233505qxX2Go5e9SIuyAT7.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.7140625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605233506QEbpXJFKm0APZNxt.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.7140625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605233506D3SEk7XOIbaMqZ02.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.7140625\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\n\n\n"}